{"word":"ἑσπέριος","slug":"ἑσπέριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑσπέριος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἕσπερος'><el>ἕσπερος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>of Time, <i>at even, at eventide</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; <el>ἑσπέριος ἦλθεν</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of Place, <i>western</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>occidentalis</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>τὰ ἑσπ.</el> <i>the western parts</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}